T1  - Manager wealth concentration, ownership structure, and risk in commercial banks
AU  - Sullivan, Richard J.
AU  - Spong, Kenneth R.
JO  - Journal of Financial Intermediation
VL  - 16
IS  - 2
SP  - 229
EP  - 248
PY  - 2007
DA  - 2007/04/01/
